Summary form only given, as follows. Experience state-of-the art design through the eyes of two experts that help shape these advanced chips! In this unique dual-keynote, the design process at two leading companies will be discussed. The speakers will cover key challenges, engineering decisions and design methodologies to achieve top performance and turn-around time. The presentations describe where EDA meets practice under the most advanced nodes, so will be of key interest to both designers and EDA professionals alike.